Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------op--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这份真情实感　好想将它传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不沉溺于一去不返的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}紧紧拥抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷于那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方应该有什么正等待着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝着那未完结的故事　飞奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀着一颗真诚的心向着那千难万险之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}张开心灵的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循环传递着一个讯息　幸福就存于这胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下来的少许勇气　尽管须以眼泪相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但这或许正是变强的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温暖的迭句　想要永远将这份珍重守护
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心绪交织　感受着这其中的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以说没有人是孤身只影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片蓝天下　好想将这份真情实感传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀揣着内心深处收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}跃入未知的前方　那里有什么正等待着我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是与未来共鸣　不断忆起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就会生出勇气　就能变得坚强　也就不再是独自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（让你倾听）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定会与你相遇　我会带着真诚的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接梦想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与其坐拥这无限的时刻　倒不如追赶那绚烂的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　总有一天会让你倾听那梦中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好冷啊  好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  大早上起来就这么多牢骚的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷就是冷  有啥不对的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是说也不会变暖和的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我来做一些热乎的小点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天反正中午学校就放学了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了！太狡猾了！只有春香你最狡猾！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天也决定中午就放学回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁愿意一天都待在学校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  不要无视！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  搬家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊  听说今天隔壁会有新的邻居搬来住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:29.77,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第3碗  招待的夜晚悄悄来临
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是冷酷无情的学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说得那么事不关己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能做的完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒假这才刚刚结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就突然布置这么多家庭作业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:03:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也就是说要培养蠢货的话  只能靠数量来培养了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是越来越讨厌学习了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才婉转的表达看起来不够明了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  诶  你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说起来  这的确是很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候我们大家要齐心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人要完成的话的确很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家一起来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个主意或许不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来  集合地点就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋你家真是无比舒适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你还真是特地来享受舒适的么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是茶室  所以我们准备留宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自作决定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来完成的话  很快就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然做决定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说今天就要来么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我就先回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  回家社团的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有社团活动真是不走运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家是打扫屋子还是洗衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…先洗衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  螃蟹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个季节  牡蛎也是很不错的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最基本的我还是觉得应该是鸡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  你在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到寒冷时节的乐趣  那必然是火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都带上神秘道具  关灯之后一起扔到锅里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使夹起来抹布也一定要吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就稍微有点那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我们来尝试一下吧  火锅聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说不定很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火锅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香喜欢火锅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说我和南春香中间隔着一个火锅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们都汗流浃背
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我帮南春香擦汗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后南春香把我的汗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会…感冒的哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新来的邻居  看起来搬家好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这个世界如此不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  初次见面  我是南
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里  我们才是请您多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你无视我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不能去玩  有好多作业要完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？一班也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二班也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是要在我们家完成作业
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人越多越有趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要认错目标哟！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅是写作业而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得带上睡衣哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在那里过夜的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要弄错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的只是完成作业而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  告诉你个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说会有转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生还是女生？去哪个班级？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没用的废物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是好事  那就去调查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷淡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实为口腹之欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就是这样  大家决定在一起写作业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起写作业似乎感觉很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  虽然说一半成分是被逼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  叫四五个人左右可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？家里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是会带睡衣来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带睡衣来的话  是说要住在这里过夜么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起留宿啊  睡衣聚会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  不  只是完成作业而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  睡衣聚会是哪个国家的节日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我不认为那是什么节日之类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候啊  睡衣节
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也留出一周的时间让我们准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是什么节日  只是大家一起完成作业而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我说啊春香  作为主人  总是要准备一点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就让我来把这次盛典搞得火热吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…到底能不能来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我该做一些准备工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算了  夏奈  乖乖给我坐在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  可是准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好不要跟今天的盛典扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想被你那些鬼点子给耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个庆典要由我来主办！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让客人感觉到无趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们南家的颜面何存！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都说了不是什么盛典
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是完成作业而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  今天晚上就吃火锅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好有好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊  火锅  一家团聚的基础啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  饭菜也由我来操办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我出门买东西了  你们在家好好看门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火锅…团聚…家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我也开始准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说隔壁的邻居搬进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个什么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不关心么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是冷淡的说法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后可能会经常见面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得应该先去打个招呼比较好么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样想的话你自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来这打招呼是年长者该做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是春香的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有资格说别人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过既然你都这么说了  不觉得自己很没责任感么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定我们这么说话的时候  对方已经过来打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:10:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这俩家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就不开门了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  进门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘁  跟我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是不明白你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这打扮很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好考虑下TPO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（TPO：分别代表时间（Time）、场合（Occasion）和地点（Place），\N即着装应该与当时的时间、所处的场合和地点相协调。）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  还是PTO来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么PTA之类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么千秋家就这么舒适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是享乐异世界么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我再躺一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  可没有时间那么悠闲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  赶紧换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才五点刚过…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢  盛典已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛典是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿…嘿…嘿…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:20.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  准备操办的人回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好半路遇见  于是就让他们帮忙提东西回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  马上就准备好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你的忙  春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  应邀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁邀你来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我叫他来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个跟藤冈没有关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天不是要吃火锅么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被火锅所召唤来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我并不这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么  夏奈又开始犯蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然连床都铺好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作真迅速啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道做无聊的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈她也想加入的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要是想加入的话早就自己跑进来加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你们怎么都换好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连床都铺好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赶紧换衣服的话会被骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都来齐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  冬马  为什么不换睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有带睡衣来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有正装的话会很为难的  客人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我住手  你这个性骚扰大婶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你比任何人都这么在意睡衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你看  我们不是主人么  不是要招待客人么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你因为是妹妹的聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不好意思直接说自己要加入么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以加入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就弱弱地奉送一句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是要留宿  才五点就穿睡衣太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这该死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶碗…是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就用那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这里的也可以用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  火锅的话已经拿过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们开始吃火锅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次火锅聚会由我来主持
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没有意见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最开始是肉类和鱼  放进去的时候要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然差不多的话就一起进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…我理想的火锅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韭菜和生菜也要放进去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了  诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了来打扰您真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚搬来隔壁  所以来拜访您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好沉我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他大概是长子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了你很沉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很有礼貌的少年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多给我闪开吧你  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这是给您的一点小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是劳您费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是羊羹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是毛巾或者肥皂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在招待客人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  不过实际上是我们家的孩子在闹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  要是还没有吃晚饭的话一起来吃吧怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸已经做好晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系  就在这里吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  真的不用了  我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  春香  那家伙是长子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是跟他爸爸两个人住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来是一个很不错的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好饱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难看的  不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被藤冈同学看见的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是春香  作为主人招待得真完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有在听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别去捣乱  大家都是来写作业的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是捣乱  这是招待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要去理会夏奈  她只会添乱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只提醒我呢  跟大家说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是因为你是最让人担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要交换吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像阿珍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们四个人一起洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱家的澡盆有那么大么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个澡盆大概勉强可以挤进去三个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想要一个可以悠闲地洗澡的浴室呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看谁先泡昏…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小…想要…比赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小…比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小…想要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵感来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的招待就是…牛奶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定会心存感激喝下这牛奶的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:18:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  什么是招待？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是细心地招待！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有我考虑的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要通过细心照顾来引导他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个  我去烧洗澡水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  洗澡水已经烧好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～来试试新的香皂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  你还真的是…嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  有不要脸的色大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我滚出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底谁是最成熟的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我使浴室燃烧了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再及时送牛奶去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:19:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来似乎是变热闹了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…哈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  内田  你第一个洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝点牛奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可会喝坏肚子的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  千秋  要不要喝点牛奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好热  口渴死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么可以喝的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那个是…牛奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有水果味儿的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我睡觉去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我差不多也该…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没有睡衣的家伙回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有喜欢的人么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚这才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要继续下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  接下来是大人的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子禁止进入喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么标准？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么标准的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:12.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（有一点儿  算是有  有） 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:15.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一点都没有）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…「有」和「没有」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝接受这个标准
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马不是男的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  我可是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了  真是  放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少比千秋更女生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多给我睡觉去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么  睡衣盛典现在才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  该起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是充实的一个盛典呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真的很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊  只要那个蠢货不在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  大家作业都做得怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家知道秋天的七草么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡枝子  芒草  葛花  瞿麦  败酱草  兰草  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天七草是为了祈祷健康而食用
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而秋天七草则是边感觉残暑消退边欣赏的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.80,0:23:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有什么华丽的植物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很不错的风俗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.87,0:23:45.54,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(370,0)}第4碗  「可以收拾了吗？」
